    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Lamps in which light, or radiant energy near the visible spectrum, is produced by the passage of an electric current through a vapor or a gas.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
